      },
      "description": "Selected-range totals from generation_usage_hourly for the mutually exclusive Core API stream. Core means a successful authenticated, non-cached generation that is neither attributed to a trusted BYOP client nor served by a community model. Paid is revenue-bearing consumption; Quest is free consumption.",
